# 📚 MySQL Stored Functions (5)

Stored Functions return a **single value** and can be used inside SQL queries.

| Function                   | Returns | Purpose                                       |
| -------------------------- | ------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| **GenerateHealthID()**     | VARCHAR | Generates a unique Health ID for each patient |
| **GenerateQueueToken()**   | INT     | Generates the next queue token number         |
| **CalculateBillTotal()**   | DECIMAL | Calculates total bill amount                  |
| **AverageDoctorRating()**  | DECIMAL | Returns average doctor rating                 |
| **CalculateWaitingTime()** | INT     | Estimates patient waiting time                |

